#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/welcome.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"RetroHexChat is a web-based IRC client with an authentic retro look and "
"feel. It supports channels, private messages, text formatting, nick "
"services, and much more."
msgstr ""
"RetroHexChat是一個基於網絡的IRC客戶端,具有真實的retro外觀和感覺. 它支持頻道,私人信息,文本格式化,暱稱服務,以及更多."

